The number of people in the room with you who have the same birthday as you.

This number is best considered as a [_]{$natural}{5}.

END_PGML

############################################################
# Solution
############################################################

BEGIN_PGML_SOLUTION
We know that the number of people must be a counting number, and since _you_ are in the room with yourself, there is at least one person in that room with your birthday. So the natural numbers are the appropriate set.

END_PGML_SOLUTION

